Description_lang: Dematrixes the target enemy's matter. When this effect is removed, the target swaps places with its most distant ally and Arcane damage equal to the target's maximum health is split between them. The portion of the total damage shifted to the target's ally increases each second.
AuraDescription_lang: Inflicts $w1% of your maximum health to you and $w2% to your most distant ally when removed. In addition, you swap places.
